  <entry>
    <title>C++标准库介绍之std::optional与std::expected</title>
    <link href="https://minecraft1248.github.io/2023/11/25/2023-11-25-C++%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%BA%93%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E4%B9%8Bstdexpected/"/>
    <id>https://minecraft1248.github.io/2023/11/25/2023-11-25-C++%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%BA%93%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D%E4%B9%8Bstdexpected/</id>
    <published>2023-11-25T13:42:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-11-25T15:04:53.442Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[  <div class="note-large red">    <div class="notel-title rounded-t-lg p-3 font-bold text-lg flex flex-row gap-2 items-center">      <p>注意</p>    </div>    <div class="notel-content">      <p><strong>本文所涉及内容所需最低C++标准：C++23</strong></p><p><strong>在尝试本文介绍的所有内容前请首先检查自己使用的C++编译器/标准库实现是否已经支持该标准或文中涉及内容</strong></p><p><strong>关于C++编译器/标准库实现对各个标准当中内容的支持状况可参阅<a class="link"   href="https://zh.cppreference.com/w/cpp/compiler_support" >cppreference <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></strong></p>    </div>  </div><h1>介绍</h1><p>如果你要写一个<strong>有可能失败</strong>的工厂函数，你会用什么工具来向函数的使用者传递函数“失败”的这一消息呢？</p><p>有的人说，我们可以用返回一个<code>bool</code>来指示函数是否成功，并且通过函数参数里的指针来返回工厂函数的结果：</p><p><em>本文中代码中的<code>flip_a_coin()</code>函数会等概率地随机返回<code>true</code>或<code>false</code>，用于模拟函数执行中有可能发生的错误，因为该函数的实现与本文主要内容无关，故不在正文中给出其实现，若有感兴趣的读者可以在文末附录找到该函数的一种可能实现。</em></p><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Cpp"><figure class="iseeu highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;print&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">some_struct</span> &#123;    </span><br><span class="line">    std::string str;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">factory_pointer</span><span class="params">(some_struct* out_some_struct)</span> -&gt; <span class="type">bool</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">flip_a_coin</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    *out_some_struct = some_struct&#123;<span class="string">&quot;factory_pointer&quot;</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; <span class="type">int</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    some_struct s;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">factory_pointer</span>(&amp;s)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s.str);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>当然，这种过时的方式的缺陷也非常明显：<strong>非常容易忘记判断返回的<code>bool</code></strong>。如果我们忘记检查函数是否成功执行就直接使用<code>out_some_struct</code>指针所指向对象的值，就有可能发生各种内存访问相关的错误。就算你可以给函数加上<code>[[nodiscard]]</code>属性，但<code>[[nodiscard]]</code>作为一个属性，它所能做的无非只是给出一行不痛不痒的warning。因此，这种方法的实用程度不高，我们需要一种方式来<strong>强制</strong>函数的使用者检查函数是否执行成功。</p><p>这时候有的人就要说了，那我们抛出<strong>异常</strong>不就行了嘛？</p><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Cpp"><figure class="iseeu highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;print&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdexcept&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">some_struct</span> &#123;    </span><br><span class="line">    std::string str;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">factory_exception</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; some_struct </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="built_in">flip_a_coin</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">throw</span> std::logic_error&#123;<span class="string">&quot;:(&quot;</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> some_struct&#123;<span class="string">&quot;factory_exception&quot;</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; <span class="type">int</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">auto</span> s = <span class="built_in">factory_exception</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s.str);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">catch</span>(std::logic_error&amp; e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, e.<span class="built_in">what</span>());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>想法很美好，但是现实是C++的异常是需要解开调用栈的，这是一种相对低效的操作。如果你的函数在代码中被大量使用的话，使用异常会带来可观的性能下降。因此，我们需要一种既强制函数使用者判断函数是否执行成功，又高效，最好简单清晰的方法。</p><p>这时候就要请出我们本期的主角了：<code>std::optional</code>和<code>std::expected</code>：</p><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Cpp"><figure class="iseeu highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;optional&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;print&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">some_struct</span> &#123;    </span><br><span class="line">    std::string str;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">factory_optional</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; std::optional&lt;some_struct&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">flip_a_coin</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> some_struct &#123;<span class="string">&quot;factory_optional&quot;</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> std::<span class="literal">nullopt</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; <span class="type">int</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">auto</span> s = <span class="built_in">factory_optional</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s.<span class="built_in">value_or</span>(<span class="string">&quot;empty&quot;</span>));<span class="comment">//print &quot;factory_optional&quot; if function succeeds, otherwise print &quot;empty&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//if statement can also be used</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(s.<span class="built_in">has_value</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s-&gt;str);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;empty&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>当然，在现实场景中我们往往不仅需要通知函数的使用者函数的执行情况，还要在执行失败的情况下给出错误原因，这时候<code>std::expected</code>就派上用场了：</p><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Cpp"><figure class="iseeu highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;expected&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;print&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;random&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">flip_a_coin</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; <span class="type">bool</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    std::random_device r;</span><br><span class="line">    std::default_random_engine e&#123;<span class="built_in">r</span>()&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    std::uniform_int_distribution&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; uniform_dist&#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="type">bool</span>&gt;(<span class="built_in">uniform_dist</span>(e));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">some_struct</span> &#123;    </span><br><span class="line">    std::string str;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">factory_expected</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; std::expected&lt;some_struct, std::string&gt; </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">flip_a_coin</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> some_struct &#123;<span class="string">&quot;factory_expected&quot;</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">flip_a_coin</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> std::<span class="built_in">unexpected</span>(<span class="string">&quot;invalid_argument&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">flip_a_coin</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> std::<span class="built_in">unexpected</span>(<span class="string">&quot;bad_alloc&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> std::<span class="built_in">unexpected</span>(<span class="string">&quot;other_error&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; <span class="type">int</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">auto</span> s = <span class="built_in">factory_expected</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s.<span class="built_in">value_or</span>(some_struct&#123;<span class="string">&quot;empty&quot;</span>&#125;).str);<span class="comment">//print &quot;factory_expected&quot; if function succeeds, otherwise print &quot;empty&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//if statement can also be used</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(s.<span class="built_in">has_value</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s.<span class="built_in">value</span>().str);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        std::<span class="built_in">println</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>, s.<span class="built_in">error</span>());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h1><code>std::optional</code></h1><h1><code>std::expected</code></h1><h1>附录A：<code>flip_a_coin()</code>函数的一种可能实现</h1><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Cpp"><figure class="iseeu highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;random&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">auto</span> <span class="title">flip_a_coin</span><span class="params">()</span> -&gt; <span class="type">bool</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    std::random_device r;</span><br><span class="line">    std::default_random_engine e&#123;<span class="built_in">r</span>()&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    std::uniform_int_distribution&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; uniform_dist&#123;<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="type">bool</span>&gt;(<span class="built_in">uniform_dist</span>(e));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
